Package: normalizeme
Title: Min-Max Normalization of data 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Luna", "Vester", , "luna@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package adds a function to normalize data using the min max scaling formula and comes with a few other functions to quickly plot your data. It does need to run with ggplot2 and the tidyverse package.
